      <hedline>
        <hl1>Boom Box</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Evan I Schwartz letter on Michael Lewis's August 13 article on new cable TV choices (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>I very much enjoyed Michael Lewis's article (Aug 13). But let's get real: the mass market has already been blown apart, thanks to all the new cable choices, the Internet and our busy lives.</p>
        <p>Evan I. Schwartz  Brookline, Mass.</p>
      </block>
